Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:38.95,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget, looking up at the sky from this hilltop,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.95,0:22:47.42,Song,,0,0,0,,The morning sun so beautiful, on spring days, just us two.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.39,0:22:55.59,Song,,0,0,0,,All the hardships and the sorrows,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.56,0:23:03.77,Song,,0,0,0,,Carry them away gently from this hilltop,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.44,0:23:10.71,Song,,0,0,0,,together with the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:21.12,Song,,0,0,0,,This vast, blue sky—may it never change,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:30.73,Song,,0,0,0,,And may my dearest friends stay just the way they are.
